This directory contains Alembic database migration scripts.

Alembic manages incremental schema changes to the SQLite database on the
PHC gateway. When the backend's ORM models (db/models.py) are updated,
a new migration script is generated and applied on the next gateway startup.

Migration workflow:
  1. Modify db/models.py with the schema change
  2. Run: alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"
  3. Review the generated migration script
  4. Test in CI: alembic upgrade head
  5. Deploy to gateway: migration runs automatically on startup

Migrations are forward-only in production (no downgrades).
